      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification test suite and version-controlled release process consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 was used. The solver has a documented verification and validation test suite covering turbomachinery flows. Version control and release notes are publicly available. Software quality assurance level 2 is achieved."
    },
    {
