      "rationale": "Three meshes (4.2 M, 12.1 M, 31.8 M elements) were generated with systematic refinement ratio r ≈ 1.45. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI below 2.3% for NIH at all five operating points on the 12.1 M production mesh. Discretisation error level 2 is achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
