      "rationale": "All five PIV and hemolysis bench-test operating points are documented with traceable measurement uncertainty (flow rate ±1.5%, speed ±0.5 RPM, fluid viscosity ±2%). Simulation boundary conditions replicate experimental values within stated uncertainties. Test conditions level 2 is achieved."
    },
    {
