      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics (mean absolute error, RMS error) must be reported for velocity fields and NIH; both must meet pre-specified acceptance thresholds.",
      "rationale": "Velocity field MAE below 8% and RMS below 12% at all PIV stations. NIH predictions within ±15% of bench-test mean across all operating points. Pre-specified acceptance thresholds met. Output comparison level 2 is achieved."
