      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, explicit iterative solver error quantification beyond residual monitoring is not required. Residuals converged to below 1×10⁻⁵ for all equations at all operating points, satisfying the minimum expectation. Formal solver error assessment scoped out at this MRL."
    },
