      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; turbulence model selection justified by literature precedent.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-ω turbulence model and power-law hemolysis model are standard choices for centrifugal blood pump CFD, supported by multiple published validation studies. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. Literature justification documented in technical report."
    },
    {
