      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; nominal input values traceable to manufacturer specifications and literature.",
      "rationale": "Geometric inputs derived from FDA-published CAD model. Fluid properties from published bovine blood data at 37 °C. Hemolysis model constants from Giersiepen et al. (1990) as widely adopted in literature. Formal input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2; a screening sensitivity study performed during model development confirmed that impeller tip clearance and rotational speed are dominant drivers, results archived in the supporting technical report."
    },
